<bibRefCitation author="Dominguez, E." box="[808,1035,1741,1765]" pageId="2" pageNumber="377" pagination="63 - 71" refId="ref6701" refString="Dominguez, E. (2009) Overview and phylogenetic relationships of the two-winged genera of South American Leptophlebiidae (Ephemeroptera). Aquatic Insects, 31, 63 - 71. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 01650420802518077" type="journal article" year="2009">Domínguez, 2009: 70</bibRefCitation>
